<AbstractNarration>The workshop titled ``Radical Innovations of software and systems&lt;br/&gt;engineering of the future'' to be held October 7-11, 2002 at&lt;br/&gt;Universita' Ca'Foscari di Venezia in Venice, Italy, will bring&lt;br/&gt;together leading researchers in all aspects of Software and System&lt;br/&gt;Engineering with a view towards discussing potential research topics of&lt;br/&gt;tomorrow.  To accomplish this goal, the workshop will have several&lt;br/&gt;talks and several open discussions, with the hope that the latter&lt;br/&gt;would lead to cross-fertilization of ideas from several disparate&lt;br/&gt;sub-areas of Software and Systems Engineering.&lt;br/&gt;</AbstractNarration>
